    <title>Git的绑定与连接</title>
    <url>/2023/10/29/Git%E7%9A%84%E7%BB%91%E5%AE%9A%E4%B8%8E%E8%BF%9E%E6%8E%A5/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h1><span id="git-de-bang-ding-yu-lian-jie">Git的绑定与连接</span><a href="#git-de-bang-ding-yu-lian-jie" class="header-anchor"></a></h1><div class="toc">

<!-- toc -->

<ul>
<li><a href="#pei-zhi-git-de-user">配置Git的User</a></li>
<li><a href="#shi-yong-ssh-fang-shi-yuan-cheng-lian-jie-git">使用SSH方式远程连接Git</a></li>
</ul>
<!-- tocstop -->

</div>

<h2><span id="pei-zhi-git-de-user">配置Git的User</span><a href="#pei-zhi-git-de-user" class="header-anchor"></a></h2><p>打开Git Bash（或命令行）</p>
<p>配置全局name：</p>
<ul>
<li><p>github用户名</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git config --global user.name name</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>
</ul>
<p>配置全局email：</p>
<ul>
<li><p>github邮箱：</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git config --global user.email email</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>
</ul>
<p>以我自己的github账户为例：</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git config --global user.name t3uk1</span><br><span class="line">git config --global user.email xxx@qq.com</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>



<h2><span id="shi-yong-ssh-fang-shi-yuan-cheng-lian-jie-git">使用SSH方式远程连接Git</span><a href="#shi-yong-ssh-fang-shi-yuan-cheng-lian-jie-git" class="header-anchor"></a></h2><p>打开Git Bash（或命令行）</p>
<p>在本地生成对应邮箱的<strong>SSH RSA公钥密钥</strong></p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">ssh-keygen -t rsa</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>使用<strong>默认生成路径</strong>，<strong>默认空key</strong></p>
]]></content>
      <categories>
        <category>Git</category>
      </categories>
      <tags>
        <tag>github</tag>
        <tag>SSH连接</tag>
      </tags>
